       true,
       "inspect.getmembers_static.__name__.__eq__('getmembers_static') == True — the function name is 'getmembers_static'; added in Python 3.11 as a descriptor-safe variant of getmembers; str.__eq__('getmembers_static') returns True; new to extra116"]
